Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.31,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Touko, Yana-chan's here for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.54,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yana-chan?
