Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.50,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,The fifty-meter freestyle.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.00,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I broke thirty-two seconds the other day!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.06,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm trying for thirty-one by fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.21,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Wow, nice going, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.21,0:03:26.29,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,You too! You're working hard toward your dream modeling job, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.89,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm cheering for you from the sidelines!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.63,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Man, you've got a great figure!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.63,0:03:32.99,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.96,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Why, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.30,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Let's go clothes shopping sometime.\NI'll pick out some outfits for you.{"I'll help you choose." if too long, though that's kind of meh}{need to shorten this or merge with previous}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.95,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.20,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Of course! I'd love to!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.32,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Oh, Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.82,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Sorry for dropping by out of the blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.47,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Let's chat outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.94,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,See you later, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.00,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.96,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,About the thing with\NYuki-kun yesterday...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.84,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You slapped him...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.77,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,He kind of asked for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.38,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I think Kakeru-kun crossed a few lines too.{think it follows on better this way. slapping him would be considered crossing one kind of line, so the fact that he crossed lines as well makes it seem more justified}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.50,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,"Kakeru-kun", huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.15,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.46,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.89,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Man, you're such an open book.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.90,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Am I really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.60,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.15,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yuki's pretty dumb, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.15,0:04:26.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.36,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Doesn't he get that he doesn't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.76,0:04:33.71,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Sachi's going back to the hospital today. {any way to shorten?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.21,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah. She said it's just for some checkups.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.90,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing to worry about, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.90,0:04:43.86,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,We'll have to watch how often we visit so we're not too much of a bother.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.79,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want to interrupt a lovers' meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.87,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.17,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,She seems to be doing fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.17,0:05:03.70,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.20,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.57,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I think she'd be happy if we went to visit her.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.49,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.33,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.66,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.14,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It's been hard to get a hold of everyone lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.14,0:05:55.87,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Something's been up since that David guy appeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.04,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,All ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.00,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,One cola.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.64,0:06:07.22,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Y'know, the visiting hours at the hospital are really short.{end early}
