Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.77,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,All right, I'm going to head home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.16,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,If there's anything you need, give me a call, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.45,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh? Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.00,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.50,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Is this your friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.50,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,This is Hiro-kun, my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.38,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.40,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. I'm Sachi's mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.77,0:06:52.89,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you. I'm Shirosaki Hiro,\NSacchan's b-boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.26,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,My grandfather baked these cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.89,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.38,0:07:25.36,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I had no idea there was a swallow's nest here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.51,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, look! Chicks!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.71,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.51,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,There are at least two of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.51,0:07:44.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You seem to know a lot more about this place\Nthan I do, even though I've lived here way longer.{You seem to know a lot more than me about\Nthis place, even though I've lived here way longer.}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.00,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's kinda depressing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.74,0:07:53.36,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I just know a few things. Living here your whole life is far more impressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.45,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,No way! You're amazing in your own right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.16,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I kind of embarrassed myself in front of you.{I showed an embarrassing side of myself to you.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.96,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.64,0:08:11.55,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Actually, Yana-chan came over to my house earlier,\Nand we talked about what happened yesterday.{trying to avoid repetition of 'day'}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.05,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You're really close friends.{can we shorten this? (26 cps)}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.93,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um... and what are we?{changed from last ep prev}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.93,0:08:21.93,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh?
