Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I couldn't face you for a second there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.17,0:08:37.50,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you think we've become more than just\Ntwo people who share the same weird power?{this line. it hurts.}{indeed}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.54,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.46,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I just saw a vision of you falling!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You'll be safe like this, though, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You can't change the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.77,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.17,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You'll be safer that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.10,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Come to the beach tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.38,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.40,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh my god, he's coming!
