Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.37,Glasslip-Main,Girl3,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.20,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,That guy is one of Onee-chan's friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.19,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.42,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.36,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Have you talked to him?
