Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.36,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I think he's involved in some complicated stuff though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.35,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh? What's he doing?
