Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.01,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,If you need anything, give me a call.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.42,0:10:25.53,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,Oh, but I'm leaving for a week-long training camp in two days,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.58,Glasslip-Main,Coach,0,0,0,,so call me either before\Nor after that if you could.
