Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.05,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I saw Yukinari-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.41,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,We can see him run past our pool at the same time every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.41,0:11:20.61,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,And somehow he ended up as our club's idol.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.69,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,They were going on about forming a fan club for him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.81,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.19,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yuki-kun's always so popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.66,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,It's a small world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.04,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yuki-kun's pretty handsome,\Nso I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.46,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,You said it! He looked really \Ngraceful when he was running.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.33,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah, he sure does.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.51,Glasslip-Main,HIna,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Why do you ask? Nothing happened, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.85,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Wow, Onee-chan, you're a terrible liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.23,0:11:49.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.99,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I need to go see Sacchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.16,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I gotta head off too!
Comment: 10,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.86,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,They need to run some more tests today.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.37,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Ah, do they?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.77,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Guess I'll head home, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.00,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,No problem. See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.43,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.23,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.23,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.69,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.94,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.20,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Great, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.95,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Oh, those are—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.15,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Hang on, lemme guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.01,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,A gift from Hiro-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.01,0:12:54.71,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Was I right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,You were.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.34,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,So, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.94,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Right, Okikura-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.76,0:13:08.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,And then Kakeru-kun said something kinda inappropriate, so Yana-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.17,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.68,0:13:16.65,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.28,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,They say the good weather will hold out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.85,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm hoping that if we watch the sea together, something...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.78,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.61,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.61,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm hoping that I might be able to see something new.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.32,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,"See something"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.16,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,You mean those sparkly things?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.00,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,When I'm with Kakeru-kun, I feel like I'm beginning to understand what they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Once I find out something more solid,\NI'll be sure to tell you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.61,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.09,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Do you think he's feeling sick?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.55,Glasslip-Main,Girl2,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.70,Glasslip-Main,Girl3,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.95,Glasslip-Main,Girl3,0,0,0,,What if the teacher comes?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.53,Glasslip-Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Hina?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.60,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.79,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm Fukami Touko's sister, Fukami Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.75,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.26,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Please don't stop being cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.63,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Please don't stop being cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.74,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It's not about the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.87,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,What's up, Sacchan?\NWhy're you calling so late?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.87,0:15:27.78,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I want to see the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.86,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'll be discharged tomorrow,\Nso what if we all went in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.47,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'd like to see Yukinari-kun and Yanagi-chan too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.24,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,We could light some\Nfireworks that night, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.57,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sure. That sounds like a lovely idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.57,0:15:43.04,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Sorry for the short notice. I'll let Touko-chan know.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.02,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.78,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'll ask Yanagi-san and Yukinari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.15,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,So, what're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.65,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Dunno...{i assume this is meant to not answer his question}{it might just mean "dunno" or "hmm"?}{making this an answer for now, kill me later}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.48,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You didn't reply to my text last night.\NYou can come, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.36,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Yanagi-san said she'd be coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.03,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.71,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Don't give me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.80,Glasslip-Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.37,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,What are you doing, man?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.38,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,He's with his girlfriend at the beach, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.29,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.82,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,I raised him to be quite the oddball.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.13,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh? I dare say he's turned into quite the charming fellow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.14,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,And I dare say that's not something his mother would point out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.85,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,So, have you thought about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.95,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,They need to run a few more tests on her,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,so they're extending her stay until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.37,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.48,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,Sachi, I thought I told you about this yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.97,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.15,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.16,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,You've made things difficult\Nfor your poor boyfriend now, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.10,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.69,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, "boyfriend"...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.25,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.95,0:17:05.62,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,I'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.21,0:17:10.87,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.82,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,Take care of Sachi for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.82,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.45,0:17:22.73,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess I should let \Neveryone know the beach trip's off.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.52,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I don't like David.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.49,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh? You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.23,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.70,0:17:31.73,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Whenever he's around, we all fall apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.28,0:17:36.87,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's true that we haven't all been together for a while now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.30,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,So what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.24,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Wanna go tomorrow instead?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.44,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Today, Touko-chan's on a date with David at Hinode Beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.44,0:17:44.95,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.68,0:17:48.99,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't ask Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.29,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.81,0:17:58.61,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,But... doesn't that mean that you tried to get us all\Nto crash their date because you don't like David?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.38,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.93,0:18:06.14,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,And you asked {\i1}me{\i0} to invite everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.11,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sacchan, does this mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.03,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.16,Glasslip-Main,Kid,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.63,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.26,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,I'll take you home!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.71,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.34,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll let him know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.29,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,The beach trip's off for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.79,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.25,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,The beach trip's off.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.53,0:19:18.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.39,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I don't mind waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.86,0:19:24.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Feeling uncomfortable?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.23,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,From the sound of the waves.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.98,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I guess it's a little different than before.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.34,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I think this is the first time I've come to the beach at this time of day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.61,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,These are for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.43,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Glass beads?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.53,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,They match mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.36,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.87,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,There's something that I've been thinking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.71,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.38,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You said I'd fall, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.38,0:19:51.64,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Right. You're not allowed\Nto go anywhere high up, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.35,0:19:55.09,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you really think that's going to happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.09,0:19:55.58,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.75,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,In the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.75,0:20:02.22,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'd have to avoid any and all places\NI could fall from for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.01,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.33,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.53,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I wonder if that really was\Na fragment of the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.53,0:20:14.65,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But you were the one who told me that they were, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.15,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Maybe we should reconsider the possibilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.40,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm going to go buy some drinks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.56,0:20:22.73,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Water, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.73,0:20:29.02,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Y'know, I've always thought it was odd that adults would pay for a drink from the vending machine,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.60,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,just to get water or tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.66,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,They could always buy\Nthe Halpis Water next to it.{Killing the "I mean" for readability}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.30,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.30,0:20:50.96,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You got invited out here too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.31,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You're not with Touko?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.81,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,She went to buy drinks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.06,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.90,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Well, I might as well say this now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.81,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It's all your fault that Yuki's not cool anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.89,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.83,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna leave now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.51,0:21:14.96,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.04,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You guys deserve each other.{chop the "really" if too long}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.21,0:21:25.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.22,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:22:00.09,0:23:30.55,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.92,0:23:32.93,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of explaining to do later.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.44,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Well, I won't ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.07,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko! What's wrong?
